name: Lago del Rio Yguazu
description: Dense agriculture plots and geomorphology patterns in Alto Paraná, Paraguay. The colorful processing output depicts relative crop development within a 3 month period. Shades of blue and green indicate early growth stages while yellow and red is related to mature and sown crops. Raw data consists of signal gathered in the visible and infrared part of electromagnetic spectrum. Input data from Sentinel-2 MSI instrument courtesy of ESA and Copernicus.
